## Call Preparation Checklist
- [ ] account number available
- [ ] payment amount known
- [ ] due date known
- [ ] hardship summary drafted
- [ ] questions listed in advance
- [ ] notebook or tracker open during call

---

## Questions to Ask
- what hardship options are available on this account?
- is there a temporary payment reduction option?
- is an extension or deferment available?
- can the due date be changed?
- will interest continue to accrue?
- how will the account be reported during the hardship arrangement?
- what happens if no arrangement is made immediately?
- can the options be sent in writing?
- what is the deadline to accept an offered option?

