## Risks
- waiting too long to call
- misunderstanding verbal offer terms
- agreeing to a plan without understanding accrual or reporting impact
- missing a deadline to accept an option
- failing to document who said what

---

## Mitigation
- call early
- ask for terms in writing
- repeat back what you heard during the call
- log the call immediately
- use the comparison table before agreeing to anything

---

## Notes
This file is meant to reduce confusion and help compare lender options clearly. It should be updated after every call, portal message, email, or mailed notice.
